Text: Re smubetas New memberBrothers George and Justin Welcome to the Beta eWooglin groupOr as most people here in Houston say BienvenidosI was the former scholarship chairman of the Gamma Omega chapter inMy main contribution to the chapter was to initiate the comparison of the semester grade point averages of the pot smokers vs the drinkers There was a spirited competition and a much awaited well attended Monday night meeting when the winning team was announced It was always closeWe remain a pretty tolerant bunch as we reach our late s and early s The parts of my college life that I remember were excellent This is a fun bunch of guys and I enjoy keeping up with them kai from Joe Storthz wwwstorthzfinancialcom Original Message From George Pereira To Sent Sunday October AM Subject smubetas New member Brother Betas I am George Pereira from the graduating class of Justin told me of the Beta group and I was so impressed that you have stayed in contact for all this time that I wanted to join Im now working in Houston where there is a nice conglomeration of recently graduated SMU Betas Do youll have anything planned for Homecoming I remember last year that there was a big Beta tent kai Get your FREE download of MSN Explorer at intlasp At Homecoming the BETA TENT had the biggest crowd by far Stay connected and consider a future homecoming BETA reunion Its incredibleforget the years in betweeneveryone just seems to pick it up right where they left off years ago Your use of Yahoo Groups is subject to infoterms Yahoo Groups Sponsor FREE COLLEGE MONEY CLICK HERE to search scholarships PvpGDmCAAySSFAAVkqlBTM At Homecoming the BETA TENT had the biggest crowd by far Stay connected and consider a future homecoming BETA reunion Its incredibleforget the years in betweeneveryone just seems to pick it up right where they left off years ago Your use of Yahoo Groups is subject to infoterms

Re smubetas hot Dog Space I saw my fellow Arkie Dent at a book signing in downtown Houston during The Junction Boys tour When are you coming back to Htown for the new book Jim Can I buy you a refreshment By the way Dent is not the only author in our ranks Written under the pen name SmackNabb I have a Beta big brother who is going throughout Texas hawking his new book The Complete Infidels Guide to Radical Islam If your local bookstore is out of stock buy Dents book kai from Joe Storthzwwwstorthzfinancialcom Original Message From Tom Hosman To Sent Saturday November PM Subject smubetas hot Dog Attached is the annual Beta Theta Pi wives tribute to Scott McNabb held at all homecoming football games I am sorry I missed this years event but I was visiting my home state watching Nebraska beat Oklahoma not that anyone cares Oh by the way Mr Dent is doing a great job hocking his book up here in Oklahoma Yesterday I heard him on talk radio KTOK where he was signing books and predicting Oklahoma to beat Tulsa to He didnt miss it by much Oh another by the way we need more Betas from the class of commenting as my gag reflex is getting to much of a workout from the class of Love Space I think Ulrich was in our pledge classOh for older Oh Fos monitoring this WOOGLIN site my brother in law John Evans Petree had his second grandchild last month hot Dog At Homecoming the BETA TENT had the biggest crowd by far Stay connected and consider a future homecoming BETA reunion Its incredibleforget the years in betweeneveryone just seems to pick it up right where they left off years ago Your use of Yahoo Groups is subject to the Yahoo Terms of Service Yahoo Groups Sponsor ADVERTISEMENT IMAGE IMAGE At Homecoming the BETA TENT had the biggest crowd by far Stay connected and consider a future homecoming BETA reunion Its incredibleforget the years in betweeneveryone just seems to pick it up right where they left off years ago Your use of Yahoo Groups is subject to the Yahoo Terms of Service

YahooGroup is not working or you are not communicating So this message is a Search for ExtraTerrestial Intelligence among the select Betas that make up this august group I will even count terrestial intelligence this time What with Homecoming only days away we figured there would be some message traffic on eWooglin Hit reply when you see this message to let me know if there is life out there kai
